{"tid":605710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抄到足】強國「維他牛」檸檬茶 扮香港品牌博懵","createTime":"2018-03-26T02:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T07:26:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":241,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ef9591bf5a586c0382a08db68611d6002de9cc","tid":605710,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180325/large/1521993176_32e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F1521993176_32e7.jpg&h=0394b86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地充斥山寨產品，近日網上熱傳寫有「維他牛」「WEITANIU」字樣的飲品，包裝盒有簡體字寫着「檸檬茶味飲料」，且標明是「香港品牌」，其包裝用色和構圖配搭，與香港品牌「維他檸檬茶」包裝十分相似，惹來網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n網上資料顯示，生產「維他牛」檸檬茶的企業是中山市維他牛飲料有限公司，地址位於廣東省中山市東鳳鎮。其官網介紹，維他牛食品集團股份有限公司於2012年10月在廣東中山組建，公司董事長黃先生在台灣興辦實業多年。產品不但有檸檬茶，還有乳酸菌、香蕉牛奶、芒果汁、功能飲料等系列！<br />\n<br />\n不過網站展示的檸檬茶包裝沒有「香港品牌」及「港牌新版」等字樣，換成「真茶+真檸檬」，而宣傳海報更寫上「要來就來真的」。有網民指，香港品牌的「維他」檸檬茶，其宣傳口號就是「真茶+真檸檬」和「要來就來真的」。質疑「維他牛」檬茶味是否是構成侵權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180326/57995011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57995011&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0927bf4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57995011&h=8cf4b82e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180326/57995011</a>"},{"pid":"9385d330af441aa3727e18e5c54871719ef31ece","tid":605710,"uid":157138,"like":467,"dislike":6,"score":461,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"抄都抄得柒過人 乜撚野維他牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498a2cb3049328ff421688c14d9000da61458706","tid":605710,"uid":4525,"like":474,"dislike":5,"score":469,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:03:53.